Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.76,0:00:16.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛丽亚 玛丽亚在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.67,0:00:22.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路易达阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.41,0:00:25.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炖小腿肉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.55,0:00:29.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不小心多做了呢 就想分给你些
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.02,0:00:32.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来 这是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.65,0:00:43.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是婴儿的拨浪鼓吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.55,0:00:46.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是谁给的…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.28,0:01:01.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,威利 过来帮我搬东西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.33,0:01:03.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.65,0:01:06.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…个 少爷的内裤…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.82,0:01:09.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,田中 上次的事件呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.08,0:01:13.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 一切都按少爷的指示
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.64,0:01:15.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.66,0:01:20.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经做好在那里住宿的准备了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.91,0:01:21.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.83,0:01:29.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来 少爷 我们去哪旅行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.61,0:01:33.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你连那种事都不知道还来收拾行李吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.42,0:01:36.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴黎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.95,0:03:11.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个执事 解约
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.37,0:03:19.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女王殿下应该是在大约在三天前到达了巴黎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.77,0:03:22.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在正在视察万博会的会场
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.42,0:03:25.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想必酒店的警戒应该很严
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.90,0:03:26.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.31,0:03:29.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少爷？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.07,0:03:31.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.25,0:03:34.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您的心不在这里对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.66,0:03:37.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刘说过了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.47,0:03:43.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陛下要挑起欧洲的…不…世界的战争
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.27,0:03:46.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是去觐见女王的理由吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.68,0:03:48.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.98,0:03:49.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.32,0:03:53.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是为那个叫阿巴莱恩特的人的死感到悲伤吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.28,0:03:55.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.64,0:03:57.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部都是我的棋子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.42,0:04:00.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要再靠近我了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.77,0:04:01.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.73,0:04:03.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.01,0:04:08.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个棋子无视了我的命令 烦人地干涉了进来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.91,0:04:10.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刘也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.26,0:04:15.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不把握住棋子的意图和战力的话 是玩不成游戏的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.17,0:04:17.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.55,0:04:25.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从埃菲尔塔入场
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.32,0:04:31.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战神广场的会场里美术宫和各国的展览馆林立
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.60,0:04:37.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,运用了大量的铁架和玻璃 充分展现技术结晶的机械展馆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.20,0:04:40.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特罗卡迪罗广场是农业展
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.16,0:04:45.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在第二会场荣军院广场里正在举行殖民地博览会
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.13,0:04:52.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其内容包括吴哥窟遗迹的重现 民族舞蹈 人类动物园
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.87,0:05:01.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与往年不同的是从美国来的牛仔还会进行西部荒野巡回演出
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.13,0:05:09.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难得的万博会 也为了新商品的开发 再稍微四处转转吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.40,0:05:12.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.45,0:05:15.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 惊奇宫里好像有天使的标本出现
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.17,0:05:17.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那真是值得一看呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.26,0:05:19.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天使的标本？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.28,0:05:28.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊 只不过是猴子而已吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.82,0:05:29.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.85,0:05:30.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去下个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.76,0:05:42.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.49,0:05:47.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.52,0:05:49.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少爷 冷静下来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.11,0:05:49.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.32,0:05:56.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在黑暗中生存下来的您的话 这点程度的黑暗根本不算什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.45,0:05:59.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.36,0:06:03.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少爷请去会场外面避难
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.85,0:06:09.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在黑暗中奔跑一点也不难
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.02,0:06:14.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的灵魂一直在黑暗中奔跑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.60,0:06:15.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.51,0:06:17.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏尔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.54,0:06:18.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏尔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.35,0:06:20.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从那天开始
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.74,0:06:21.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到现在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.99,0:06:24.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在黑暗之中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.57,0:06:26.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑暗…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.19,0:06:42.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好耀眼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.93,0:06:47.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里真的是我生活的世界吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.25,0:07:19.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 这么慌张
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.36,0:07:25.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.60,0:07:28.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏尔 好久不见了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.72,0:07:30.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女王殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.59,0:07:45.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.16,0:07:47.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里的风景
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.43,0:07:52.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想在新世纪之前 将欧洲改变
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.18,0:07:54.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.69,0:07:57.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里有点脏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.81,0:08:01.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里有污秽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.47,0:08:05.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里也很不洁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.66,0:08:10.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有将全部破坏一次的必要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.01,0:08:13.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不破坏就没有创造
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.32,0:08:16.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了迎接洁净的新世纪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.08,0:08:19.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我国将吹起席卷一切的风
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.10,0:08:24.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法多姆海恩府是我净化的哟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.72,0:08:36.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多么恶趣味啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.46,0:08:44.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.19,0:08:56.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在…这里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.55,0:08:53.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伦敦大桥正在倒下来 倒下来 倒下来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.04,0:08:56.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs20\an8}伦敦大桥正在倒下来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.26,0:09:00.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs20\an8}我美丽的小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.95,0:09:00.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直在找的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.22,0:09:11.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想让您告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.95,0:09:12.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.65,0:09:18.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么不仅仅是杀掉 还要制造出那么悲惨的场景
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.59,0:09:20.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能将危险放置一旁不顾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.02,0:09:23.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏尔 那是净化哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.98,0:09:27.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轻蔑死者是您所谓的净化吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.91,0:09:29.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我轻蔑了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.36,0:09:30.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.00,0:09:37.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轻蔑 我… 对一直以来对我尽忠的法多姆海恩…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.15,0:09:40.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少能一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.60,0:09:41.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.85,0:09:56.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您吃惊了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.65,0:09:59.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简直像是散发着年轻气息的少女一样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.88,0:10:00.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚修
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.89,0:10:08.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陛下在幸福的半途中失去了心爱的丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.26,0:10:16.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陛下哀叹着夫君的死 一度也曾想了结自己的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.56,0:10:27.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「为了能与心爱的夫君一起永远地生活下去」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.29,0:10:33.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我将陛下的身体与夫君的身体连在了一起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.28,0:10:36.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将身体…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.63,0:10:43.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道夫君对我做出的行动感到高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.47,0:10:47.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样夫君的身体就…怦怦地在跳着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.35,0:10:52.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怦怦 生命的跃动
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.44,0:10:58.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与相爱的人在真实的意义上合为一体的那种喜悦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.48,0:11:01.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想赠与法多姆海恩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.64,0:11:06.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其死决不会成为凄惨之物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.76,0:11:08.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是这么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.70,0:11:18.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陛下与夫君拥有将英国指引向纯净世界的强烈的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.50,0:11:26.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其志向将自己的污秽一扫而光 成为了这样纯洁的少女
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.27,0:11:29.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多么崇高的志向
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.18,0:11:32.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正适合作为由天使服侍的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.16,0:11:35.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天使？难道你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.75,0:11:40.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚修 至少让夏尔在你的刀刃下终结
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.41,0:11:45.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚修的刀刃是非常美丽的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.12,0:11:49.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简直就像是新世纪升起的朝日光辉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.23,0:11:52.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以智慧之荣耀拔剑出鞘
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.71,0:11:56.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将你体内的野兽驱赶出来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.53,0:11:59.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再把它推进深渊中去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.34,0:12:02.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愿你有纯白色的来世
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.03,0:12:05.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏尔·法多姆海恩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.16,0:12:15.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使是自己擅长的剑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.95,0:12:18.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,击不中的话也是没有意义的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.05,0:12:20.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.42,0:12:23.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许这就是终点了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.03,0:12:27.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 请下令
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.50,0:12:31.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏尔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.55,0:12:34.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将亚修…杀死
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.11,0:12:38.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仅有这些…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.04,0:12:43.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将女王…杀死
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.32,0:12:44.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏尔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.58,0:12:45.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.90,0:12:58.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多么可怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.74,0:12:59.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏尔 拜托
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.30,0:13:01.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让他停下来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.86,0:13:02.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏尔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.66,0:13:08.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.25,0:13:08.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.61,0:13:09.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.14,0:13:15.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手 塞巴斯蒂安
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.58,0:13:18.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.92,0:13:20.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让别人看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.65,0:13:23.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去 只会增加骚乱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.84,0:13:25.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那只是普通的人类
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.04,0:13:28.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要在意呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.60,0:13:30.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 就此撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.11,0:13:38.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天使的翅膀…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.97,0:14:08.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么让我停下来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.50,0:14:10.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经说过了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.55,0:14:12.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会引人注目 仅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.62,0:14:14.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.06,0:14:16.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.10,0:14:22.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的愿望是对让自己落入地狱之人的复仇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.73,0:14:28.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那日的誓言是怎么说的？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.74,0:14:32.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您将我唤醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.85,0:14:35.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个事实永远不会变
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.25,0:14:38.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经付出的代价永远不会回来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.19,0:14:41.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 选吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.66,0:14:42.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,命令
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.39,0:14:49.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀了他
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.02,0:14:58.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我将成为您的剑 帮您完成复仇的心愿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.77,0:15:00.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其代价为
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.75,0:15:03.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灵魂什么的 不论多少都让你吃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.19,0:15:05.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毫无犹豫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.04,0:15:06.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.60,0:15:13.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那日的您应该没有犹豫的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.33,0:15:18.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然知道了事实 还要向女王尽忠吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.96,0:15:22.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从一开始就没有对她的忠诚心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.70,0:15:26.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是作为法多姆海恩家的主人行动罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.21,0:15:30.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 您是舍不得自己的灵魂了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.37,0:15:33.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要灵魂来做什么 真啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.87,0:15:34.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.19,0:15:43.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天好像累了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.54,0:15:46.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到了驿馆后 请好好休息
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.79,0:15:52.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是让人讨厌的城市
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.38,0:16:01.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从那天开始 照顾我穿衣起居就成了你的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.79,0:16:08.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让恶魔来模仿执事的工作 你做得还真是漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.47,0:16:11.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为法多姆海恩家的执事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.46,0:16:16.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闲聊就到此结束
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.72,0:16:19.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多该休息了 少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.36,0:16:28.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请忘记一切 愿您有个幸福的美梦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.47,0:16:47.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏尔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.44,0:16:49.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏尔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.89,0:16:56.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有再一次获得未来的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.02,0:16:58.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再一次…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.08,0:17:04.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舍弃女王的看门狗这一称谓
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.31,0:17:07.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舍弃一直怀抱的仇恨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.55,0:17:09.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再一次…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.80,0:17:20.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塞巴斯…蒂安
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.10,0:17:23.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塞巴斯蒂安
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.31,0:17:25.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塞巴斯蒂安 去哪了 早上的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.76,0:17:27.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听不到我说话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.53,0:17:36.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塞巴斯蒂安！！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.59,0:17:42.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是702室的法多姆海恩 随从去哪了知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.89,0:17:45.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 请稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.55,0:17:58.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,印记没有消失 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.56,0:18:02.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请忘记一切 愿您有个幸福的美梦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.66,0:18:07.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙才不会希望我有什么幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.26,0:18:11.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 「忘记一切」是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.09,0:18:13.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.08,0:18:15.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诀别
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.28,0:18:22.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回到伦敦之类的事 我自己一人也能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.97,0:18:30.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将我带到加莱的港口去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.47,0:18:35.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈 小子 那是拜托别人的态度吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.02,0:18:37.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要多少
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.12,0:18:49.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.31,0:18:50.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.48,0:18:52.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说的是去加莱的港口才对
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.89,0:18:56.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思呢 不巧我家是反方向呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.17,0:18:58.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.67,0:19:03.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布洛涅港口的话 就往反方向一直走
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.42,0:19:06.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正 慢慢地拐来拐去的话 迟早会到的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.36,0:19:08.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.72,0:19:10.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做出和我给你的代价相应的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.36,0:19:43.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一晚 拜托
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.74,0:19:45.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.09,0:19:47.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在没有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.12,0:19:49.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到了伦敦再补寄给你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.72,0:19:54.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.08,0:19:58.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道我是谁吗 夏尔·法多姆海恩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.73,0:20:00.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是哪的小贩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.68,0:20:02.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道法多姆海恩公司吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.13,0:20:06.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看这个指环 是法多姆海恩代代相传的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.82,0:20:09.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么就这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.38,0:20:13.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用那个指环做代价就让你住下来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.45,0:20:15.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挺不错的石头呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.33,0:20:17.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早餐也给你做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.33,0:20:18.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.67,0:20:24.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开什么玩笑 区区一个便宜旅馆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.74,0:20:35.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肚子饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.91,0:20:43.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好冷 来这里来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.53,0:20:52.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 连你也要耍本少爷吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.98,0:20:54.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.80,0:21:06.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这么近的地方…有港口
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.51,0:21:15.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使这样我也 那样彷徨着 没有找到它
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.18,0:21:20.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明…在如此近的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.58,0:21:56.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,着火了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.53,0:21:58.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水…水…去拿水
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.31,0:21:58.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是

